data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 4BR/2.5 Bath home w/NO REAR NEIGHBORS located in beautiful Westheimer Lakes. This home truly offers the complete package for comfortable, stylish & convenient living providing ample space for family/guests. RECENT ROOF-RECENT HVAC-RECENT WATER HEATER allow peace of mind & energy efficiency for yrs.  Other features include recent carpet & wood-look tile floor downstairs w/upgraded light fixtures. The Kitchen is a chef's dream w/under-cabinet lighting & lots of bright cabinets w/generous counter space. Upstairs are 3 spacious BR's, a bathroom, & large GAMEROOM w/custom safety rails. Situated on a large lot, the sprinkler system keeps the lawn looking its best year-round while the WiFi-enabled garage door opener provides added convenience/security. TOP-RATED SCHOOLS, LOW TAX RATE/easy access to Westpark Toll Rd, close proximity to shopping & restaurants, a well-designed floor plan, & great neighbors make this opportunity one you do not want to miss!
